opic，鳩估twitter &gt; reddit / quora<br />\n3. Search得多數對件事有興趣想知，通常較易convert<br />\n4. Quora好多印度人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 以上純參考，個人都覺得twitter, reddit &gt; quora，有心有力做埋quora無壞<br />\n<br />\nReddit<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/reddit.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexa.com%2Fsiteinfo%2Freddit.com&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=c22f1573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/reddit.com</a><br />\n排名19<br />\n4成search traffic<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpWYOmF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpWYOmF.png&h=4dd3dd93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/twitter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexa.com%2Fsiteinfo%2Ftwitter.com&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=3907be92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/twitter.com</a><br />\n排名48<br />\n15%search traffic<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAWemHk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAWemHk.png&h=049acaca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQuora<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/quora.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexa.com%2Fsiteinfo%2Fquora.com&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=697c5788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/quora.com</a><br />\n排名245<br />\n7成search traffic<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nhnk1H5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnhnk1H5.png&h=a655d436&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"171344b61d04bf13012dec63f94f77fc1ccbd4cb","tid":2039493,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"Quora 小粉紅, 紅心蕉大把, 已經放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24021470124bef4447f16f4b2d898e5759c93168","tid":2039493,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d7aca6e178a5bb3438e9c96bbe47682a7bc8b01","tid":2039493,"uid":286897,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"32bc7d2cb6fd22d51a37f6b55c9b01945ecbe59f","tid":2039493,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"Quora係一個美國既網站，專比唔同人問問題，再等人比答案你。（乜鳩問題都可以問）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個月有3億瀏覽量</span><br />\n<br />\n而近來強國網軍開始進攻Quora，用撚左好多假accounts/有時直情用普通話拼音既名黎留言，不斷扭曲事實。（屌你個閪你同我講你係英國人然後你個名係<em>John Smith? Harry Bloom?</em>作都作個好D既名啦屌你)<br />\n<br />\n大家如果download左個app, search &ldquo;China&rdquo; &ldquo;Hong Kong&rdquo;，再比幾分鐘睇下，就會知咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mmarcnh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmarcnh.png&h=2f791452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姓Liao既香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHJDNXm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHJDNXm.png&h=1ccce16f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟英文好過好多垃圾強國人，依排係Quora戰鬥左好耐，但葉問都係一個打十個啫，黎左十一個就會打死葉問啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懇請大家幫幫手。有好多用Quora既人係外國人。一search &ldquo;Hong Kong&rdquo;就會冇辦法地被洗腦，我地需要盡下力阻止中共網軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><br />\n同我download Quora. 同我入去用真相反擊班撚屌五毛</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"不如成立一個tg gp 打擊佢哋！<br />\n最緊要人多可以控制download upvote<br />\n同埋最緊要有一啲寫手專門寫文<br />\n1編1編咁嚟啦！<br />\n我可以幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開咗個group 幫得手嘅入嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n專係downvote upvote ge 專題寫手嘅都ok<br />\n<br />\n光復一篇得一篇<img src=\"/asset